    "attributes": {
        "action": "Protect Child Tax Credit renewal for Key Workers working extra hours covid19",
        "additional_details": "Some NHS and Key Workers will be in receipt of these types of benefits and will be working additional hours as Leave, Bank Holidays and covering sickness is required and this will impact 2021 renewals.The system will financially penalise those classed as Key Workers and required to go to work by the very same Government that order it.",
        "background": "In April 2021 those on benefits will need to renew them by submitting their income details. Do not financially penalise those that are NHS and Key Workers that are being required to work additional hours during Covid19 2020.",
